snippet.title: 「Fate/stay night REMASTERED」Release Announcement PV
snippet.description:
Seek the root of the Fate franchise. Return to where it all began.

Fate/stay night REMASTERED release in August 8, 2024
*This title is a remaster of the original PlayStation Vita title "Fate/stay night Réalta Nua" and is available for the first time in English and Simplified Chinese

【Official X】
@ Fate_SN_Game
https://twitter.com/Fate_SN_Game

© TYPE-MOON

Platforms：PC (Steam), Nintendo Switch
*Available for download only.

Release：August 8, 2024
Languages：English, Japanese, Simplified Chinese
